    <item>
      <title>耶伦称赞美国经济强劲，赞扬拜登的政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/yellen-touts-strong-us-economy-in-praise-of-biden-s-policies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[即将离任的财政部长珍妮特·耶伦坚决捍卫拜登政府的政策选择，强调美国经济相对于主要经济体的强劲表现、以及过去的表现和更为悲观的经济学家预测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/yellen-touts-strong-us-economy-in-praise-of-biden-s-policies</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将在特朗普回归前的告别演讲中强调就业增长和政治遗产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/biden-to-tout-job-growth-legacy-in-farewell-address-before-trump-return</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登将在他的告别演讲中把自己的总统任期描述为经济复苏，希望在共和党选举失败且民意调查显示他的支持率跌至新低之后确定自己的政治遗产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/biden-to-tout-job-growth-legacy-in-farewell-address-before-trump-return</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的交通运输选择承诺减少繁文缛节，优先考虑安全</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/trump-s-transport-pick-vows-to-cut-red-tape-prioritize-safety</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据唐纳德·特朗普周三在参议院听证会上发表的讲话，他选择领导美国运输部，并计划告诉立法者，如果得到确认，他将减少阻碍大型基础设施项目进展的繁文缛节。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/trump-s-transport-pick-vows-to-cut-red-tape-prioritize-safety</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
